	<h1 class="title">启发了那么多中国真人秀的《美国偶像》会如何结束？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/112251/small/112251.png?1431932514" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">纽约时报 John Koblin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-18 08:35:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9473/medium/9473.jpg?1436680365" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


